name: SpaceFlights
0:
”Alexa open Space Flights and tell me which is the next space launch.”
”Alexa open Space Flights and tell me the names of the astronauts who are in space.”
”Alexa open Space Flights and tell me who is in the ISS.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: space flights
des:
This skill is based in the Launch Library API and Space Launch Now API. Space Flights provides you information about space launch events like:
- When is the next space launch, who is launching, which rocket model is and information about the mission.
- You also can ask which is the next rocket launch for your favorite Space Agency like SpaceX.
- Also you can ask for the current crew of International Space Station.
- And even you can know how many astronauts are currently in Space Missions.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
